                        <h3>Lac-Mac,&nbsp;established in 1920, remains North America&rsquo;s leading manufacturer of reusable protective technical products for various market segments.</h3><p>We specialize in&nbsp;quality, high-performance, liquid-proof, breathable&nbsp;PPE products.<br />For more than 30 years we have been&nbsp;a trusted licenced manufacturer for&nbsp;products using a family of&nbsp;GORE&reg; technical&nbsp;fabrics. Additionally, we manufacture protective products under our exclusive R.MOR.Tex&reg; brand for the operating room.&nbsp;All of our products can be custom designed to meet customer specifications.</p><p><a class="learn arrow" href="/about-lac-mac/manufacturing-and-quality-systems">Learn More</a></p>                            <!--<h3>Lac-Mac celebrates 94 years in business</h3>
